{"id": 2595, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你的版权意识主要体现在哪儿？", "description": "尊重版权、尊重原创，其实可以体现在挺多小事上啊。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock ）", "record_count": 15075, "comment_count": 75, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181030111746hq0JR6Oox9KP5Q1F.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-01T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4866, "title": "现如今你的版权意识主要体现在哪儿？", "content": "现如今你的版权意识主要体现在哪儿？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 308036, "content": "心疼钱也还是买了正版游戏、正版软件", "image": "img/option/option/20181101102717zZaIfOiVQDKG68bt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 308037, "content": "想看电子书直接上亚马逊买，不先搜书名+pdf", "image": "img/option/option/201811011024599jwG4R2fUguQKzpF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 308038, "content": "不跟人分享视频账号、或者购买的原创知识产品", "image": "img/option/option/20181101102802hBG7yKNT3tU0pQn5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307583, "content": "听歌、看电影都会充会员，不东找西找下资源", "image": "img/option/option/20181030111138iMN7OspkVUylj08T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307584, "content": "转发有出处的图片，会主动带上@或者水印", "image": "img/option/option/201810301111541E0maPRkhg5Q8pHI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307585, "content": "遇到侵权现象，会帮事主转发或者@事主", "image": "img/option/option/20181030110739vdA3gsWOXDjwbYnJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307586, "content": "不看抄袭的电视剧和盗版的综艺节目", "image": "img/option/option/20181030111851zZT8I30HkAeUS9fF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307587, "content": "发现“洗稿文”，之后都会避开这个作者", "image": "img/option/option/20181030111430dGtbTNQL8OpkJFrj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307591, "content": "跨平台搬运视频之前，先去问问up主是否同意", "image": "img/option/option/20181030111456mZefRTw76dFKqayL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 307601, "content": "购买原创的知识付费产品", "image": "img/option/option/2018103011